,"body":"うむうむ、人生何事も経験ですぞ～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event114-03-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"ねーねー、バイトの話はいいからさ！\n置いてないか、早く聞いてみようよ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event114-03-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"あっ、そうでした～。\n実は私、あるお菓子を探してるんです～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event114-03-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"何かシリーズものの食玩らしくって。\nいや、まあ多分、置いてないと思うんですけど……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event114-03-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"どうぞ、しっかり見てください。\nこの画像のお菓子に見覚えはありませんか〜？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event114-03-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"モカ・リサ","body":"ほほ～……\nうわっ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"event114-03-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"リサ","body":"ちょ、ちょっと不気味な見た目のお菓子だね……\nけど、どこかで見たことあるような……\nモカ、陳列した記憶ある？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event114-03-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"モカ","body":"お菓子のパッケージとは思えない色合いですな～。\nあたしは見たことないですー","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event114-03-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"リサ","body":"だよね、アタシも並べた記憶ないし……気のせいかな。\nゴメン！　多分うちでは扱ってないと思う！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event114-03-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"そっか～、残念。\nあっさり見つかると思ったんだけどな～。\n人気商品なんだよね？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event114-03-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"もちろん、話題沸騰の大人気商品ですよー。\n雑誌に大きく書いてあったのをちゃんと目撃してますから〜","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event114-03-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"……ちなみにさ、七深ちゃん。\n何の雑誌に紹介されてたの、それ？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event114-03-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"先月の『超自然との出会い』ですよ～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event114-03-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"モカ・リサ","body":"…………？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"event114-03-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"（リサさんもモカちゃんも、\n全然知らないって顔してるな……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event114-03-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"（てかタイトルからしてめちゃめちゃ胡散臭いんだけど……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event114-03-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"あ、あれ？　みなさんもしかして\n『超自然との出会い』をご存じない……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event114-03-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"あっ、あたしそれ知ってるよ！\n今日も持ってるし！　ほら、これでしょ！？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event114-03-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"え、持ってるんですか！？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event114-03-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"これ、よくわかんない陰謀論とか、地球空洞説とか、\nとにかく変なこといっぱい書いてあって、超面白いよね！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event114-03-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"やっぱりオカルト系の雑誌なんですね……\nていうか日菜さん、そういうの読むんですか？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event114-03-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"ほら、前にあたし達SFっぽい映画撮ったでしょ？\n不時着した宇宙船から地底人を助けて、\n元いたところに帰してあげるって話","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event114-03-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"リサ","body":"あー、なんかモグちゃん？　だっけ？\nモグラの地底人が出てくる映画だよね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event114-03-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"そうそう！\nその撮影の時に、小道具として置いてあったのが、\nこの雑誌なんだよね～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event114-03-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"で、それ以来たまに買って読んでるんだ～。\nけど、まさか七深ちゃんも\nこれ読んでるとは思わなかったな～","ten